<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Community Deletion Notice</title>
  <style>
    /* Copy styles from welcomeEmail.ejs and modify as needed */
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://thecapitalhub.in/static/media/logo-white.c4e4dacf1f6283c93e11.png" alt="CapitalHub Logo">
    <h2>Community Deletion Notice</h2>
    
    <p>Dear <%= memberName %>,</p>
    
    <p>We regret to inform you that the community "<%= communityName %>" has been deleted by <%= adminName %>.</p>
    
    <p>Reason for deletion:</p>
    <div class="reason-box">
      <%= reason %>
    </div>
    
    <p>We encourage you to explore other communities on CapitalHub that align with your interests.</p>
    
    <a href="https://thecapitalhub.in/explore-communities" class="cta-button">Explore Communities</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The CapitalHub Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 